        {
            "title": "王毅同伊朗外長通話 促各方抓住機會窗口盡快啟動和談",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國外交部發布的新聞稿顯示，外長王毅同伊朗外長阿拉格齊通話時敦促各方盡快啟動和談進程。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">王毅強調所有熱點問題都應通過對話談判解決，而不應使用武力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「談起來總比打下去好，」王毅說。「希望各方抓住一切和平機會和窗口，盡快啟動和談進程。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">王毅的表態正值美國總統唐納德·川普在一天前稱美方正與伊朗進行談判。儘管如此，圍繞這些所謂幕後接觸仍存在混亂，包括參與方及是否可能達成協議。伊朗否認正在與美國談判，而美國防務夥伴巴基斯坦提出願意在雙方之間進行調解。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8c426755-1c30-3aea-b385-22ed3928648d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">王毅曾呼籲立即停火，並敦促國際社會加大勸和促談的努力。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據周二發布的中方新聞稿，阿拉格齊表示伊方致力於實現全面停戰而不僅僅是暫時停火。他還表示，霍爾木茲海峽對所有人開放，船隻可以安全通過，但正在交戰的國家不在考慮之列。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自美國和以色列對伊朗發動戰爭以來，德黑蘭通過打擊海灣地區能源設施並事實上關閉霍爾木茲海峽予以回應。該海峽是通往亞洲的關鍵油氣運輸通道。這導致全球能源價格飆升，並加劇市場波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：一艘中國所有的油輪沿伊朗一側航線穿越霍爾木茲海峽</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自2月下旬衝突爆發以來，通過該重要水道的船隻數量寥寥。其中包括與伊朗、中國和敘利亞有關聯的船隻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Wang Yi Pushes Iran to Talk With US About Ending War</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%8E%8B%E6%AF%85%E5%90%8C%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1-%E4%BF%83%E5%90%84%E6%96%B9%E6%8A%93%E4%BD%8F%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E7%AA%97%E5%8F%A3%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%87-162336081.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 01:36:33",
